{
  "stem": "19502.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When it was Christmas, she always said something for me on the tree, you know, because those days they gave out candies or books or something.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She always had something for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When my mother was-- was cross with me, I used to run to Pania Antiska if I cut myself [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And here she-- [SOBBING] stayed over home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We came-- we came the next day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We came to-- to the place, to where they told us to come.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He says, from now on, you all have to gather into a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they put us into a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So many people in one room, was no place where to turn around.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No food.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We have to go into another part of the town.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were some people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't even know them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, some from a village with some, so I stayed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother was-- was-- was coming too, but he was out of the town, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was working that time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I didn't know he was all the time working underground for the-- for the Russians, for the partisan.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All along he was working for the underground.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But once in a while he was able to come to the-- I mean, when he came to the ghetto, he was able to bring honey, some bread.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they allowed us for a few hours to get out of the ghetto to go to market.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Two hours a day.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But with what are you going to buy the stuff?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember I cut off buttons and I traded I think from my coat four buttons, five for some food.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I came down to this Pascha.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I came over to her and I said her, Pascha, I don't have nobody.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
